=== Config change for Stage B (application.yaml, hibernate.* properties) ===
spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.jdbc.batch_size: 50
spring.jpa.properties.hibernate.order_inserts: true
Statement.id is UNCHANGED — still @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY).

App restart log (Hibernate 7.4.1.Final, HHH100501), proves the config loaded before Stage B ran:
