=== Stage B — batch_size=50 + order_inserts=true, IDENTITY still in place (EXPECT: no change) ===
--- Run 1 ---
{"runId":9,"strategy":"FETCH_JOIN","accounts":13303,"statementsWritten":13303,"elapsedMs":45658,"statementsPerSec":291.36186429541374,"jdbcQueryCount":13325}
